<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fire is not a likely force in this alliance. Fine-scale freeze-thaw, rock fall, and drought are more apt to determine stand distribution and extent.</div>
